Denchar source is back in its own Util directory
Author: Alberto Garcia <albertog@icmab.es>

=======================================================================
Version: 1.3
Date: 2004/02/01 18:00
Title: Denchar moved to top source directory !
Author: Alberto Garcia <wdpgaara@lg.ehu.es>

Description: Denchar now lives in the top source directory. 
             The manual and Examples are stil under Util/Denchar.

