Version: 1.2.0
Date: 2003/07/03  18:30 
Title: Capability for 3D and wavefunction plots
Author: Pablo Ordejon  <ordejon@icmab.es>

Description:

  Denchar has extended its capabilities to:
 1) Produce 3D plots (in the form of Gaussian Cube files)
 2) Plot wavefunctions read from Siesta

