Version: 1.1.0
Date: 2002/02/04  16:00 GMT
Title: F90 Denchar Implementation, Compatible with Siesta-1.2.5 
Author: Javier Junquera  <Javier.Junquera@ulg.ac.be>

Description:

   A F90 implementation of Denchar code has been done.
 It included all the atomic routines by A. Garcia needed
 to read the basis from files.
 

Files: We import the following files

   Src/atmfuncs.f
   Src/atmparams.f
   Src/atm_types.f
   Src/atompla.f
   Src/basis_io.F
